{"word":"H2459 - חֶלֶב - cheleb - kheh'-leb - [idiom] best","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֶלֶב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>cheleb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kheh'-leb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] best"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கொழுமை, கொழுப்பு, உச்சிதம், நிணம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"fat (used of humans, used of animals), choicest, best part, abundance (used of products of the land)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From an unused root meaning to <i>be fat</i>; <i>fat</i>, whether literally or figuratively; hence the <i>richest</i> or <i>choice part</i>: -  X best, fat (-ness), X finest, grease, marrow."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2459 - חֶלֶב - cheleb - kheh'-leb/2459\">H2459</a>, <a href=\"#/H2460 - חֵלֶב - Chêleb - khay'-leb/2460\">H2460</a>, <a href=\"#/H2462 - חֶלְבָּה - Chelbâh - khel-baw'/2462\">H2462</a>, <a href=\"#/H2463 - חֶלְבֹּון - Chelbôwn - khel-bone'/2463\">H2463</a>, <a href=\"#/H2464 - חֶלְבְּנָה - chelbᵉnâh - khel-ben-aw'/2464\">H2464</a>, <a href=\"#/H303 - אַחְלָב - ʼAchlâb - akh-lawb'/303\">H303</a>"}]}